Why is Map Reduce faster? -- A practical example of data joins
 
 
 
Joining data with Map Reduce is the fastest, most scalable way to generate reports. 
Generating reports is a vital part of any product. Reports show how you're meeting the needs of your users. Reports tell you how much money you owe or are earning. Even  PageRank  is just a report of the best content. But generating reports at scale, on large amounts of data, is difficult.